OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny rain
OL,6,Fwill become increasingly isolated
OL,7,Fthrough the evening, mainly confined
OL,8,Fto the north of the region. It will
OL,9,Fturn largely dry for a time, although
OL,10,Fa few isolated showers may push north
OL,11,Flater, most likely around dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FAny remaining showers will
OL,14,Fsoon clear east, leaving a dry but
OL,15,Fvery warm day with plenty of hazy
OL,16,Fsunshine. Light winds will do little
OL,17,Fto alleviate the heat.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
