OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry with long sunny periods, though
OL,7,Fthundery showers may develop later on
OL,8,FThursday and persist into the early
OL,9,Fhours of Friday. Widely very warm,
OL,10,Fincluding overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
